# Per-extension CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md files generated by `swamp repo init`
# The root CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md symlink is the single source of project guidance
*/CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
*/AGENTS.md
**/AGENTS.md
# But keep the root-level symlink
!/AGENTS.md

# Git worktrees for isolated development
.worktrees/
